@startuml
title Capability Resolution
actor User
participant Orchestrator
participant Registry
participant Gateway
participant Executor
User -> Orchestrator: request capability
Orchestrator -> Registry: resolve capability
Registry --> Orchestrator: implementation candidates
Orchestrator -> Gateway: execution request
Gateway -> Executor: invoke implementation
Executor --> Gateway: response
Gateway --> Orchestrator: normalized result
Orchestrator --> User: answer
@enduml
